PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of RÉGIS RÉMILLARD, of Brossard, Quebec, as part-time director of the board of directors of the Montreal Port Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Raphael Esposito, whose term has expired.
